ames.com/pccafe\", \"description\": \"PC Cafe program details.\" }, { \"name\": \"Steam VR\", \"url\": \"https://partner.steamgames.com/doc/features/steamvr/info\", \"description\": \"Virtual Reality features.\" } ] } }, { \"id\": \"web_api\", \"title\": \"Steam Web API\", \"description\": \"HTTP-based API at api.steampowered.com. Format: /<interface>/<method>/v<version>/?key=<key>&format=<format>. Supports JSON (default), XML, VDF.\", \"content\": { \"interfaces\": [ { \"name\": \"ISteamUser\", \"description\": \"Access and manipulate Steam user information.\", \"methods\": [ { \"name\": \"GetPlayerSummaries\", \"description\": \"Basic profile info for Steam IDs (persona name, last logoff, etc.).\" }, { \"name\": \"GetFriendList\", \"description\": \"Friends list for a SteamID.\" }, { \"name\": \"GetPlayerBans\", \"description\": \"Player ban information.\" }, { \"name\": \"ResolveVanityURL\", \"description\": \"Resolve vanity URL to SteamID.\" }, { \"name\": \"CheckAppOwnership\", \"description\": \"Check if user owns an application.\" }, { \"name\": \"GetDeletedSteamIDs\", \"description\": \"List of deleted accounts that owned a game (GDPR).\" } ] }, { \"name\": \"ISteamApps\", \"description\": \"Information about applications and DLC on Steam.\", \"methods\": [ { \"name\": \"GetAppList\", \"description\": \"All applications available on Steam.\" }, { \"name\": \"GetServersAtAddress\", \"description\": \"Game servers at a specific IP.\" }, { \"name\": \"GetAppBetas\", \"description\": \"Beta branches for an application.\" }, { \"name\": \"GetAppBuilds\", \"description\": \"Build history for an application.\" }, { \"name\": \"SetAppBuildLive\", \"description\": \"Set a build live for a beta branch.\" } ] }, { \"name\": \"ISteamEconomy\", \"description\": \"Trade and economy related functionality.\", \"methods\": [ { \"name\": \"GetAssetPrices\", \"description\": \"Prices of items in a game's economy.\" }, { \"name\": \"GetAssetClassInfo\", \"description\": \"Infor